     <tr>
	      <td class="par" colspan="7">He could not obtain an Account of the general Exports from the West Indies, and therefore, cannot make a Comparison, with those from North America, which were.</td>
	      <td class="curr" style="text-align: center; vertical-align: bottom;">s</td>
	      <td class="curr" style="text-align: center; vertical-align: bottom;">d</td>
	    </tr>
